<p>The Javadoc says:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Set the position measurement period used to calculate the velocity of a quadrature or hall sensor encoder. For a quadrature encoder, this number may be between 1 and 100 (default). For a hall sensor, this number may be between 8 and 64. The default for a hall sensor is 32ms.</p>
</blockquote>
